HEADWORD: Inleague
<hw>In*league"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Inleagued</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
